<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/921442-1-why-are-the-returned-not-surprised">1. why are the Returned not surprised that their are loved ones, who remained living, aged since time went past? They don&#39;t even say things like &#39;oh you look a bit older&#39; 2. Do the bodies still stay in the graves, why does nobody dig the graves out to check this?</a>
</div>
